snippet.title: Lansquenet 2004 (Arcade/SNK/2004 Longplay) [HD]
snippet.description:
http://www.youtube.com/user/MartinKiller88/videos
Check my other longplays (mostly in HD quality) on my channel. If you really liked my videos, don't forget to subscribe. Lansquenet 2004 is a bootleg of Shock Troopers 2 manufactured by Saurus and released in 2004 for Arcades.
It's a much easier version of Shock Troopers 2nd Squad, also quite longer with different set of levels. As you see it's hard now to even lose a life in this bootleg, your Health Point bar is a lot bigger and you can collect unbelievably huge amount of bombs.
